    "status": true,
    "newFeatureTips": {
      "zh-CN": [
        {
          "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><strong>支持为 Roxy 账号登录启用两步验证</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\">现在可以绑定 Google Authenticator 等第三方身份验证器</p><div data-w-e-type=\"video\" data-w-e-is-void style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<video poster=\"\" controls=\"true\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" style=\"\"><source src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750916078936__2FA.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/></video>\n</div><p><br></p>",
          "id": "7e1575b1-eb3b-4198-aed5-c9f868a9c25f"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>支持批量创建窗口时以顺序分配的方式绑定平台账号</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750921783874__Sequential%20Assignment.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>",
          "id": "1f319fb5-4f08-4652-8710-3aae2329a85f"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>支持在项目管理中对项目进行拖动排序（调整同时会应用于 Pin 在左侧菜单的顺序）</strong></p><div data-w-e-type=\"video\" data-w-e-is-void style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<video poster=\"\" controls=\"true\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" style=\"\"><source src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750921756142__%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8B%96%E5%8A%A8%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/></video>\n</div><p><br></p>",
          "id": "d7d740da-f50f-4194-860d-7de80817f5c5"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>支持在窗口列表中通过点击表头来调整排序方式</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750921802209__Click%20to%20Sort.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>",
          "id": "2530578d-c41d-46e1-9540-085efa220951"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>优化软件整体性能及部分 UI、交互体验</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922558089__New%20Create%20Panel.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>",
          "id": "7e329d48-16b1-42bf-b273-017ace15f62c"
        }
      ],
      "en": [
        {
          "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><strong>Support for two-factor authentication for Roxy account logins. </strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\">You can now connect third-party authenticators such as Google Authenticator.</p><div data-w-e-type=\"video\" data-w-e-is-void style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<video poster=\"\" controls=\"true\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" style=\"\"><source src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750916339673__2FA.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/></video>\n</div><p><br></p>",
          "id": "924f7559-043b-4ea4-9988-a86d8702ef4d"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>Support for assigning accounts sequentially when creating profiles in bulk.</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922222730__Sequential%20Assignment.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>",
          "id": "7323db95-e27e-49e4-beff-9db6bdb75b91"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>Projects can now be sorted by dragging and dropping. (The new order will also be reflected for projects pinned to the left menu.)</strong></p><div data-w-e-type=\"video\" data-w-e-is-void style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<video poster=\"\" controls=\"true\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" style=\"\"><source src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922246532__%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8B%96%E5%8A%A8%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/></video>\n</div><p><br></p>",
          "id": "64fe049a-a0a0-4a64-b5f9-f66aa90ae576"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>Support for sorting your profiles by simply clicking on the column headers in the list view.</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922258880__Click%20to%20Sort.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>",
          "id": "44480974-171a-44cd-83de-e2f3693122c4"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><strong>Optimized overall software performance and improved aspects of the UI and UX.</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922598829__New%20Create%20Panel.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"></p>",
          "id": "f24b5531-6914-46f4-aad9-a505d5f17249"
        }
      ],
      "ru": [
        {
          "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><strong>обавлена поддержка двухфакторной аутентификации (2FA) для входа в аккаунт Roxy. </strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\">Теперь вы можете подключить сторонние аутентификаторы, такие как Google Authenticator.</p><div data-w-e-type=\"video\" data-w-e-is-void style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<video poster=\"\" controls=\"true\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" style=\"\"><source src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750916355438__2FA.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/></video>\n</div><p><br></p>",
          "id": "d66c90a1-ce19-4e8c-bac5-e75f6e2c7dfa"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>Добавлена поддержка последовательного назначения аккаунтов при массовом создании профилей.</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922293528__Sequential%20Assignment.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>",
          "id": "0d489cc5-34b4-40f9-bf4f-0d594a189714"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>Проекты теперь можно сортировать перетаскиванием. (Новый порядок также будет применяться к проектам, закрепленным в меню слева.)</strong></p><div data-w-e-type=\"video\" data-w-e-is-void style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<video poster=\"\" controls=\"true\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" style=\"\"><source src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922302181__%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8B%96%E5%8A%A8%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/></video>\n</div><p><br></p>",
          "id": "5a9abbe7-77a7-429a-b097-c8365f5f7237"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p><strong>Добавлена поддержка сортировки ваших профилей в списке простым нажатием на заголовки столбцов.</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922311181__Click%20to%20Sort.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"/></p>",
          "id": "33a0009a-986a-47e4-b79d-561c718f5528"
        },
        {
          "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><strong>Оптимизирована общая производительность ПО и улучшены аспекты UI и UX.</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><img src=\"https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/static/upload/1750922617150__New%20Create%20Panel.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"\"></p>",
          "id": "7311e89d-8e23-4eb7-affa-acf9ef6ef7d4"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
