    "upgradeDesc": "",
    "upgradeContent": "<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><strong>修复部分情况下接收窗口转移时的代理连接问题</strong></p>",
    "upgradeContentEn": "<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><strong>Fixed proxy connection issues encountered in some cases when receiving profile transfer.</strong></p>",
    "upgradeContentRu": "<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><strong>Исправлена проблема с подключением к прокси при приёме передачи окна в некоторых случаях.</strong></p>",
    "releaseTime": "2025-06-13 11:21:50",
    "downloadUrl": "https://lumibrowser.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/public/package/app/Windows/64/3.5.1/RoxyBrowser_x64_3.5.1.exe",
